snippet.title: Cat Quest: Pirates of the Purribean - Reveal Trailer | PS5 & PS4 Games
snippet.description:
Get whiskered away on a hearty catventure in Cat Quest: Pirates of the Purribean, the latest instalment in the award-winning Cat Quest series, coming to PS5 & PS4 in 2024!

Play as a swashbuckling purrivateer in this open-world action RPG set in the Purribean - a fantastical pirate-themed world swarming with Pi-rats! Alongside your trusty spirit companion, set sail through the Purribean in your very own ship and search for the Northern Star - a long-lost mythical treasure.

Wishlist now: https://store.playstation.com/10007859
